                  <formatted-text>
                    <run bold='true' fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Light' fontsize='12'>West and East together contribute 60% of total revenue (₹27.6L out of ₹45.9L), while South lags at ₹8.2L – prioritise South expansion and replicate West’s Electronics-focused strategy.</run>
